messages.subject: new interview sound file (me, last week)
messages.msgSnippet: I was interviewed last week and I made it its own page this morning with the sound file, photos and links: http://sandradodd.com/listen/schwartzinterview
messages.messageBody:
I was interviewed last week and I made it its own page this morning
with the sound file, photos and links:
http://sandradodd.com/listen/schwartzinterview

Although it's a Law of Attraction "station" (podcast), I told her I
didn't subscribe to that and it might be better not to bring it up.
But it was a fun interview and on the page I was able to expand on a
thing or two and put links.

If you do listen to it and think of other things I should write or
link, please let me know.

Today Dayna Martin is being interviewed, 11:00 PST, noon mountain
time. It will be available to listen to later, too.

Sandra

[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
